{"tid":1689102,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民抗爭]1[市民篇] 被捕攻略","createTime":"2019-11-02T16:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T02:32:50.000Z","uid":8005,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a9c06b3ca1d14465699342a772deac03dde35655","tid":1689102,"uid":8005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:31:42.000Z","msg":"眼見社會抗爭已經連續發生左好幾個月, 好多市民, 手足, 警察. 因為長時間既洗腦而唔記得左好多抗爭既重點, 我黎緊一篇一篇打出黎, 當中會有市民篇, 警察篇, IT技術篇, etc. 希望可以以德服眾, 回復平靜香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">由於依家法庭有禁制令, 本人絕對唔會發佈任何言論鼓勵或煽動暴力，意圖造成人身傷害或損毀財物 </span><br />\n不過我怕警察叔叔學歷唔夠, 記性唔好, 我想會係後面既文章, 提下你地既防守戰術重點, 同埋要保護既目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果反應好, 我會加速打文, 反應唔好可能會打慢d, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家歡迎轉載我未來既文, 但麻煩係文章前後加番<strong>黑警死全家, 光復香港, 時代革命, 五大訴求, 缺一不可</strong><br />\n<br />\nbtw 祝需要武運既人, 武運昌隆, 黑警死全家"},{"pid":"d8645bf560619e10e7547c88dd3d037f00b12b6e","tid":1689102,"uid":43033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:32:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cdde9c69d6ce714df27abd4e9ce90e053ec9391c","tid":1689102,"uid":8005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982b6b0363394a4cdbf2502142ebf669f4e7f6a6","tid":1689102,"uid":8005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8645bf560619e10e7547c88dd3d037f00b12b6e","tid":1689102,"uid":43033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:32:23.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:33:33.000Z","msg":"搶左我個#2, 未貼文呀手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d242d8095c365f2e443fdd6002e0efd12a6c93","tid":1689102,"uid":8005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DP9woBO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F